OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778940666
OL,3,CIsrael says it killed Hamas's military
OL,4,Cleader and architect of October 7
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FIsrael says it has killed the leader
OL,8,Fof Hamas's military wing, one of the
OL,9,Farchitects of the October 7 attacks
OL,10,Fthat triggered the war in Gaza.
OL,12,FIzz al-Din al-Haddad was killed on
OL,13,FFriday, Israel's army said, describing
OL,14,Fhim as one of the last senior
OL,15,Fcommanders in Hamas' military who had
OL,16,Fdirected the planning and execution of
OL,17,Fthe Hamas-led attacks.
OL,19,FThe attacks killed some 1,200 people
OL,20,Fin Israel and saw more than 250 taken
OL,21,Fhostage into Gaza.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
