PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778940666
OL,3,CIsrael says it killed Hamas's military
OL,4,Cleader and architect of October 7
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FIsrael's retaliatory strikes have
OL,8,Fkilled more than 72,700 people,
OL,9,Faccording to the Gaza Health Ministry.
OL,11,FThe ministry is part of Gaza's Hamas-
OL,12,Frun government, but staffed by medical
OL,13,Fprofessionals who maintain and publish
OL,14,Fdetailed records, viewed as generally
OL,15,Freliable by the international
OL,16,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
