CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778940666
OL,3,CIsrael says it killed Hamas's military
OL,4,Cleader and architect of October 7
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FAl-Haddad's killing comes as the
OL,8,Fceasefire between Israel and Hamas
OL,9,Fremains fragile as key issues like the
OL,10,Fdisarmament of Hamas stall the deal's
OL,11,Fprogress.
OL,13,FDespite the ceasefire, which went into
OL,14,Feffect in October, Gaza has seen near-
OL,15,Fdaily Israeli fire with more than 850
OL,16,Fpeople being killed since then,
OL,17,Faccording to Gaza's Health Ministry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
