PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778940666
OL,3,CIsrael says it killed Hamas's military
OL,4,Cleader and architect of October 7
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FAl-Haddad was the latest Hamas
OL,8,Fcommander to be killed by Israel.
OL,9,FIsrael said he had assumed the role
OL,10,Fafter his predecessor, Mohammed
OL,11,FSinwar, was killed.
OL,13,FThe army said al-Haddad had surrounded
OL,14,Fhimself with Israeli hostages during
OL,15,Fthe war as a shield against an attack.
OL,17,FAl-Haddad's family confirmed to The
OL,18,FAssociated Press his death in Friday's
OL,19,Fstrike along with six other people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
