OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778940666
OL,3,CIsrael says it killed Hamas's military
OL,4,Cleader and architect of October 7
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FHis funeral was held on Saturday in
OL,13,FGaza City. His body was wrapped in
OL,14,FHamas and Palestinians flags as it was
OL,15,Fcarried by mourners.
OL,17,FHe joined Hamas when it was
OL,18,Festablished in the 1980s, and was a
OL,19,Fmember of the Qassam Brigades' Majd
OL,20,Fsection, which was tasked to go after
OL,21,Fcollaborators with Israel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
