PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778940666
OL,3,CIsrael says it killed Hamas's military
OL,4,Cleader and architect of October 7
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FHe was also a member of Hamas'
OL,8,FMilitary Council, the highest group of
OL,9,Fcommanders that played a key role in
OL,10,Fthe attacks that sparked the war.
OL,12,FIsrael's chief of staff for the army
OL,13,Fcalled his killing a significant
OL,14,Foperation, and said Israel would
OL,15,Fcontinue pursuing its enemies to hold
OL,16,Fthem accountable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
