OL,3,CIsrael says it killed Hamas's military
OL,4,Cleader and architect of October 7
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FSince the shaky ceasefire was reached,
OL,8,Fboth Israel and Hamas have traded
OL,9,Faccusations of violations. Israel has
OL,10,Ftargeted Hamas members inside the
OL,11,Fcoastal enclave, the last of whom was
OL,12,Fthe son of Hamas' lead negotiator,
OL,13,FKhalil al-Hayya.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
